- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is a possible category as the paper discusses the semantics of metamodels, which is related to logic. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is a possible category as the paper discusses the management of complexity, consistency, and evolution of metamodels, which are relevant to database management. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper discusses the role of metamodels at run-time, which is relevant to AI systems.
